{"tid":996043,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(魔法少女小圓)QB狩獵","createTime":"2019-01-26T03:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T11:17:00.000Z","uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"242dc379c5d453e02a9503157c9ea2ae957acd86","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://f4sn.moe.hm/QB.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ff4sn.moe.hm%2FQB.html&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=77ff6c1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://f4sn.moe.hm/QB.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴哈原址<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/Co.php?bsn=43592&amp;sn=15498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D43592%26sn%3D15498&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6ed6f03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/Co.php?bsn=43592&amp;sn=15498</a><br />\nFLASH的網路小遊戲<br />\n殺QB<br />\n還蠻好玩的<br />\n注:不要發言打中文，請打英文或日文，以防被鎖IP<br />\n <br />\n玩法<br />\n上方選擇世界(伺服)<br />\n:Z攻擊 X換彈夾 C換武器 方向鍵移動<br />\nWAVE為一波攻擊(越後面越難打但越高結束後拿到的武器越好)<br />\n契約ノルマ在QB進入畫面外會削減.歸0就GAMEOVER(可以拿到武器)<br />\n最小化或切換畫面會被當成斷線(不能拿到武器)<br />\n <br />\n角色:<br />\n小圓:全素質+20,射擊武器貫穿2倍<br />\n轟姆:射擊武器射程無限,填彈數2倍<br />\n沙也加:近戰2連擊,死亡時3倍回血速度<br />\n麻美:攻擊力+50%,暴擊率+15%<br />\n杏子:近戰射程+40%,擊退+8<br />\n圓神:全素質+20,填彈+50%<br />\n眼鏡轟姆:爆彈暴風範圍+20%,攻速+30%<br />\n黑沙也加:近戰2連擊,單下損血不會高於10<br />\n小夏:走速+50%,吃掉近身的QB<br />\n仁美:死亡時發生毒瓦斯(畫面外緣損血),近戰時高機率暴擊<br />\n換角色原本的等級會減半<br />\n <br />\n素質:<br />\n魔力:攻擊力,擊退 <br />\n精神:最大血量,死亡後回血速度<br />\n敏捷:走速,填彈速度,近戰攻速 <br />\n幸運:得到道具的品質,暴擊率(暴擊=5倍威力)<br />\n伺服器並不是很穩定(像現在好像在維護)<br />\n喜歡的請好好珍惜，不要上去亂.謝謝!"},{"pid":"4761f0e02143b0c2922061cff48727c9e92967f9","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wikiwiki.jp/guee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikiwiki.jp%2Fguee%2F&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9eeda185\" target=\"_blank\">https://wikiwiki.jp/guee/</a><br />\n攻略"},{"pid":"f06f01e740a91a43b73ccb0c1a7eba5f78f7240c","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42b78c0db35c36dea8e90f07c9115331cc67520","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:19:47.000Z","msg":"一齊玩下"},{"pid":"16eb238557b3eb872eb73d5eddd1642fd6fa071c","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309b02820eaac509e7fc958b3b91b3516cfe8aee","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f1f4690ce697b0c3e730198972276210af7d8b","tid":996043,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c4827b7eba3687f55872937969ec9c47254984ef","tid":996043,"uid":104216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"5 6年前玩過 都幾難刷好裝<br />\n到而家仲未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93a1850654614eef79d33f9ec016f4143289eac","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4827b7eba3687f55872937969ec9c47254984ef","tid":996043,"uid":104216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"5 6年前玩過 都幾難刷好裝<br />\n到而家仲未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"執左<br />\n呢個SERVER繼承的"},{"pid":"cf25233a7741200a09e104589d8cc00f0db2d561","tid":996043,"uid":224429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"<